As people who love the sport of boxing and its history, this collaboration between 
@superareshop and @ringtv featuring three different Muhammad Ali covers during the 1970’s has it all! 
Check out this video piece Superare put together on what Muhammad meant to The Ring Magazine. 
The collection is now available to shop exclusively at Superare stores in NYC, LA, and online at 
superareshop.com

node.title: Superare x The Ring Magazine Presents: Muhammad Ali
